                <p style="width: 100%;text-align:right;" class="my-5">
                    Learning 3D design can be a rewarding and fulfilling experience that allows you to explore your interests, develop new skills, and push the boundaries of your creativity. Whether you're pursuing 3D design as a hobby or a career, it offers opportunities for personal growth and self-expression.
                </p>
            </th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>
                <h5 style="text-align:left;" class="mr-5">Allowing to Marketability:</h5>
                <p style="width: 100%;text-align: left;" class="my-5">
                    Proficiency in 3D design software is highly sought after in various industries, including animation, gaming, film production, architecture, interior design, product design, and advertising. Taking a 3D design course can enhance your skill set and make you more marketable to potential employers.
                </p>
            </th>
